lead_paragraph: Ronni Williams scored a career-high 26 points and grabbed 11 rebounds as No. 19 Florida rolled to a 74-51 victory over Wofford on Wednesday night.

headline.print_headline: Williams Scores 26; No. 19 Florida Women Beat Wofford 74-51
